data.description: Assumable FHA loan at 2.75% rate. This adorable "barn-style" 2 Story home near Downtown Loveland is bursting with character! Nestled on a quiet street with cute xeriscaped front yard, the exterior has great curb appeal & is all done. New roof, garage door, siding, windows, exterior doors, & stunning stone chimney. Inside you will discover all new luxury vinyl plank floors & carpet. Wonderful floor plan with 2 living areas- main level living room with wood burning fireplace & large upstairs loft! The 3 bedrooms are spacious plus there is a bonus main level office. All stainless kitchen appliances & washer/dryer set stay. Enjoy the Google doorbell, Nest thermostat, & Smart blinds also included! Fully fenced backyard with matching shed & garden beds. Don't miss the alley access & backyard gate perfect for RV/boat/trailer storage. Fabulous location close to restaurants, breweries, new movie theater at the Foundry, & more. No HOA or metro tax.
